Originally I was going to upload a torrent from another tracker, but I was stopped short since PB would not allow this.  So, instead I re-released with my own file naming using their tracker.
BTW, to clarify the left had side reading #M = #Mb, e.g.176M = 176 MB file size.  It is not part of the file name.
